parts.overview: After being whacked on the head with a shovel, Valdis no longer shows interest in the things that used to make his life worthwhile: alcohol, techno, cars and fights. His friends desperately try to help him regain his memory, but nothing works.
parts.title: Alien or: The Escape of Valdis in 11 Episodes

parts.overview: Valdis, having finished his space odyssey, is back in town. The whack from the shovel has been wiped from his memory and he remembers everything. However, Märt, Ott and the whole town have changed a lot in 20 years and there is no use in remembering. All is well though, the boys will just have to again show Valdis what makes life worthwhile.
parts.title: Alien 2 or: The Return of Valdis in 17 Episodes
